query:
INSERT INTO jobs (
                queue, job_type, payload_json, run_at, status, priority, max_attempts,
                locked_at, locked_by, lock_expires_at,
                dlq_reason_code, dlq_at,
                replay_of_job_id
            )
            VALUES (
                $1, $2, $3, $4, 'queued', $5, $6,
                NULL, NULL, NULL,
                NULL, NULL,
                $7
            )
            RETURNING id
